Quest:All Things Must Pass

From Wizard101 Wiki
Jump to: navigation, search

Quest Information


Prequest:
Don't Be Scared
Note: Level 58 is needed to start this quest.
Note: In order to complete this quest, Wizards must be in the School of Death.

Given By: Dworgyn

Giver Location: Nightside
This is a side quest.

Goals:
Go to the bridge in Nidavellir
Talk to Dworgyn in the School of Death
Hand In: Dworgyn

Reward:

400
4,500
Skeletal Dragon

Leads to:

Katzenstein Never Kloses (at level 68)

Quest Dialogue


This page is for recording a complete Quest Dialogue of all the conversation and story during a quest.
This includes NPC discussions, Narrator statements, and Creature speeches.


Documentation on how to edit this page can be found at Template:QuestInfobox/doc.

Hints, guides, and discussions of the Wiki content related to All Things Must Pass should be placed in the Wiki Page Discussion Forums.

Search for content related to All Things Must Pass in the Central Wiki Forums by clicking here.
